{
  "_comment": "OWPML / HWPX namespace map. Source: hancom-io/hwpx-owpml-model OWPML/Base/NamespacePrefix.{h,cpp}. The '2011' column is the legacy URI baked into all HWPX files produced by Hangul (still current as of Hangul 2024 — the URI literally contains '2011', but is the active version). '2024' column is the modernised OWPML 2024 URI used in newer Hancom drafts/specs; in practice, real-world .hwpx files almost always use the 2011 URIs.",
  "prefixes": {
    "hp": {
